Introduction¶

Tip: In this project we will be analyzing data associated with the TMDb movie This data set contains information about 10,000 movies collected from The Movie Database (TMDb),

The final two columns ending with _adj show the budget andrevenue of the associated movie in terms of 2010 dollars,
accounting for in flation over time
